reviewText: This video has some of the biggest bucks on tape Ive ever seen , not a typical hunting video but more a celebration of lifes sweet passions in nature . Excellent filming
Is you are a seasoned hunter, you will appreciate it.  The musing/philosophizing is a tad... off of reality and truth.. butt is a free country.

This book was for my grandson who needed it for his class in  High  School this year.  I talked to him about it and he said it was very good.  He also suggested  that I read it too, when he finished it.
